@startuml 校园搭子匹配系统 - 系统架构图
!define RECTANGLE class

title 校园搭子匹配系统 - 系统架构图

package "前端" {
  [Vue 3 前端] as Vue
  [HTML/CSS/JS] as HTML
}

package "后端" {
  rectangle "Controller 层" as Controller
  rectangle "Service 层" as Service
  rectangle "Mapper 层 (MyBatis)" as Mapper
  rectangle "Security 层 (JWT)" as Security
}

package "数据层" {
  database "MySQL" as MySQL
  database "Redis (缓存)" as Redis
}

package "外部服务" {
  [云服务器] as Cloud
}

Vue --> Controller : HTTP/RESTful
Controller --> Security : 认证拦截
Security --> Service : 权限验证通过
Service --> Mapper : 数据操作
Mapper --> MySQL : SQL
Service --> Redis : 缓存读写
Cloud --> Vue : 部署

note right of Security
  Spring Security + JWT
  无状态认证
end note

note right of Service
  业务逻辑：
  - 用户管理
  - 活动管理
  - 匹配逻辑
  - 评价计算
end note
@enduml
